  "title": "Project Planner/ Assistant Planning Manager",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Construction industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>Project Planner/ Assistant Planning Manager </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p><ul><li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li><li><strong>Position:</strong> Project Planner/ Assistant Planning Manager</li><li><strong>Location:</strong> Woodlands (Transport provided from Admiralty MRT)</li><li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 5.5 days, Office Hours</li><li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Basic + Bonus</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Develop, maintain, and update comprehensive project plans, schedules, and timelines using industry-standard software.</li><li>Monitor project progress against baselines, prepare regular performance reports, and present findings to senior management and stakeholders.</li><li>Identify and assess the impact of project scope changes on timeline, budget, and resources.</li><li>Proactively adjust and revise project plans and schedules to mitigate risks and address project variations.</li><li>Collaborate closely with operations teams, clients, and other stakeholders to ensure seamless execution and alignment throughout the project lifecycle.</li><li>Maintain meticulous documentation of all project events, variations, and issues to support contractual and obligations management.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least Bachelor’s Degree in Civil Engineering.</li><li>Minimum of 5 years of experience in a project planning or scheduling role within the construction industry.</li><li>High proficiency in project management software such as Primavera P6 and Microsoft Project.</li><li>Able to start work immediately or in short notice.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p><ul><li>Click the APPLY button, or</li><li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li></ul><p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p><p><br /></p><p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p><br /></p><p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p><p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
